section.para:
AQL
drop array To delete an array with AQL, use the DROP ARRAY statement:
AQL% DROP ARRAY A;

nulls
allowing in attributes Attributes are by default set to not null. To allow an attribute to have value NULL, add NULL to the attribute data type declaration:
AQL% CREATE ARRAY product_null <name:string NULL,price:float NULL,sold:datetime NULL> [i=0:*,10,0];
